\par }{\cs28\i\f1\cf6 Then: }{\f1\fs32 Both now and ever, and unto the ages of ages. Amen.
\par 
\par }{\cs28\i\f1\cf6 Theotokion:}{\f1\fs32  O Theotokos; thou art the true vine that hath blossomed forth for us the Fruit of Life. Thee do we supplicate:  Intercede, O Lady, together with the holy apostles, that our souls find mercy.
\par 
\par Blessed is the Lord God, blessed is the Lord day by day; the God of our salvation shall prosper us along the way; our God is the God of salvation.
\par 
\par Holy God, Holy Mighty, Holy Immortal, have mercy on us. }{\cs28\i\f1\cf6 (Thrice) 
\par }{\f1\fs32 
\par Glory to the Father, and to the Son, and to the Holy Spirit, both now and ever, and unto the ages of ages. Amen. 
\par 
\par O Most Holy Trinity, have mercy on us. O Lord, blot out our sins. O Master, pardon our iniquities. O Holy One, visit and heal our infirmities for Thy name's sake. 
\par 
\par Lord have mercy. }{\cs28\i\f1\cf6 (Thrice) 
\par }{\f1\fs32 
\par Glory to the Father and to the Son and to the Holy Spirit, both now and ever, and unto the ages of ages. Amen. 
\par 
\par Our Father, Who art in the Heavens, hallowed be Thy Name. Thy Kingdom come, Thy will be don
e, on earth as it is in Heaven. Give us this day our daily bread, and forgive us our debts, as we forgive our debtors; and lead us not into temptation, but deliver us from the evil one. 
\par 
\par PRIEST: }{\cs23\b\f1\fs36 For Thine is the Kingdom and the power and the glory, of the Father, and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit, now and ever, and unto the ages of ages.}{\f1\fs32 
