\par }{\cs27\i\f1 READER: }{\f1\fs32 Amen.   }{\cs28\i\f1\cf6 And we read the appointed Kontakion.  If there be two kontakia, we read the one that was chanted after the 6th Ode of the canons at Matins.  Then:
